re! Just let me know how I can help!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event43-11-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"... Okay, thanks.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event43-11-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Ah, but I'm no good with a sewing machine, just so you know. The last time I used one at school, the teacher got mad at me and said the thing I made looked all twisty and turn-y like the Nile River!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event43-11-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"O-oh...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event43-11-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Hey, Sayo~... Are you sure we should just be here practicing like this?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"If the others aren't going to come to rehearsal, then it's up to us to preserve Roselia's sound, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"I think the next time we play, these songs won't have a chance of coming together if no one is practicing them...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Even if we've lost the intensity that used to accompany our sound... This is still my personal sound... I have no choice but to play it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"You really have changed, Sayo. Looks like that promise you and Hina made was a pretty big deal.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"I suppose you could say that... That's why I can't allow myself to stop here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"You can't stop...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Sayo...! I think I figured it out!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Figured what out?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"How to bring Roselia back!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"I see... In other words, we were all working together as Roselia, but we all had our own personal goals in mind.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"I think so. As a band, we were supposed to be trying to reach Future World Fes, but...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Were we all actually striving for that? I feel like we were only trying to fulfill our own goals while also being a part of Roselia.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"We were all members, but maybe no one was actually looking out for Roselia as a whole...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Sayo? Sorry, I'm not very good at explaining this sort of thing...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"No, I think you got it right. I continue playing the guitar so that I can find my own sound... So that I can keep my promise to my sister...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"And that makes me wonder... Was I actually keeping the band itself in mind while doing so...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"The same goes for me. I said I was trying to help Roselia, but really, Yukina was the main one I was keeping an eye out for...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Even though we're all part of the same Roselia, I think we all had our eye on something different... Our goals weren't the same.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Remember when Rinko stormed out during rehearsal? Maybe that's what she meant when she said no one was listening.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"It's possible that Shirokane-san was the person paying the most attention to Roselia as a group.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Ako did the same. She's always talked about how Roselia is \"super cool.\" So the music we create when we all play together... I think she could be the one who treasures it the most.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event43-11-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Seems like we'll need those two to help us out if we want to bring Roselia back.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event43-11-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0}],"selectableData":[],"layoutData":[{"type":2,"sideFrom":3,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":3,"sideToOffsetX":0,"depthType":0,"characterId":25,"costumeType":"025_casual","motionName":"","expressionName":"default","moveSpeedType":0},{"type":2,"sideFrom":7,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":7,"sideToOffsetX":0,"depthType":0,"characterId":24,"costumeType":"024_casual","motionName":"","expressionName":"default","moveSpeedType":0},{"type":0,"sideFrom":3,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":3,"sideToOffsetX":0,"depthType":0,"characterId":24,"costumeType":"","motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","moveSpeedType":0},{"type":0,"sideFrom":3,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":3,"sideToOffsetX":0,"depthType":0,"characterId":25,"costumeType":"","motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","moveSpeedType":0},{"type":0,"sideFrom":3,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":3,"sideToOffsetX":